headline: Teradyne Announces Production System for Double-Sided Wafer Probe Test for Silicon Photonics
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., March 31, 2025--Teradyne, a leading provider of automated test equipment, has partnered with ficonTEC, a global leader in production solutions for photonics assembly and test, to announce the availability of the first high-volume, double-sided wafer probe test cell for silicon photonics. This innovative solution is designed to meet the growing demand for high-throughput electro-optical testing of silicon photonic wafers driven by co-packaged optics (CPO) applications.
